@startuml sequence_notes
!theme plain
title Add / Edit / Delete Note

actor User
participant "NotesPanel" as NP
participant "NotesController" as C
participant "Handler" as H
database "DB" as DB

User -> NP: type body
NP -> C: POST /api/contacts/{id}/notes
C -> H: AddNoteCommand
H -> DB: INSERT Note
H --> C: NoteDto
C --> NP: 201
NP --> User: prepend to list

== edit ==
User -> NP: edit own note
NP -> C: PUT /api/notes/{noteId}
C -> H: UpdateNoteCommand
alt author or admin/citylead
  H -> DB: UPDATE Note
  H --> C: ok
  C --> NP: 200
else
  H --> C: 403
end
@enduml
